@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accessToken = replace-me
@activityId = replace-me
@roomId = replace-me

### 현재 앱 활동 기록
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/activity/current-app
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "{{roomId}}",
  "appName": "IntelliJ IDEA",
  "windowTitle": "Bubli Backend",
  "startedAt": "2026-07-01T01:00:00Z",
  "endedAt": "2026-07-01T01:30:00Z"
}

### 오늘 활동 기록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/activity/today
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 활동 기록 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/activity/{{activityId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
